    {
      "paragraph_name": "POPULATE-AUTH-LIST",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph populates the authorization list on the screen. It moves data from the PENDING-AUTH-DETAILS segment to the corresponding fields in the COPAU0AI map based on the current index (WS-IDX). It formats the authorization amount, time, and date. It also converts the authorization response code to an approval status ('A' for approved, 'D' for denied). The EVALUATE statement assigns the authorization details to the appropriate row on the screen based on WS-IDX. The DFHBMUNP is moved to SEL000xA to allow the user to select the authorization.",
